 downward revision being too large, and the Ne\nabundance being underestimated for the Sun by about a factor of 2.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Aug 2008 07:55:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Aug 2008 09:43:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 26 Jan 2009 11:42:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
